  <entry>
    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/application-development-blog-posts/march-developer-challenge-cloudevents-it-s-a-wrap/ba-p/13654243</id>
    <title>March Developer Challenge - CloudEvents: It's a wrap!</title>
    <updated>2024-04-01T06:08:23.211000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>ajmaradiaga</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/107</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="CloudEvents-Developer-Challenge.drawio.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/76098i60480142BAFD3A00/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="CloudEvents-Developer-Challenge.drawio.png" alt="CloudEvents-Developer-Challenge.drawio.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Yesterday, we concluded March's developer challenge in the SAP Community - All about CloudEvents and event-driven architectures. Thanks to everyone who took part in it :-). I hope you had as much fun participating in the challenge as I had preparing it. &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;In case you missed the developer challenge but you are interested in knowing what it was all about... you can get started here: &lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/application-development-discussions/march-developer-challenge-cloudevents-week-1/td-p/13629129" target="_self"&gt;March Developer Challenge - CloudEvents: Week 1&lt;/A&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;If you want to learn more about CloudEvents and event-driven integrations, I would recommend keeping an eye on the content of the Event-driven integration CodeJam - &lt;A href="https://github.com/SAP-samples/events-driven-integrations-codejam" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://github.com/SAP-samples/events-driven-integrations-codejam&lt;/A&gt;, which is now close to being finalised :-). Also, remember that you can request/host an SAP CodeJam event in your city or company, and we will be happy to help you run it - &lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam-blog-posts/so-you-want-to-host-a-codejam-everything-you-need-to-know/ba-p/221415" target="_blank"&gt;https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam-blog-posts/so-you-want-to-host-a-codejam-everything-you-need-to-know/ba-p/221415&lt;/A&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Are you wondering about what will be April's Developer challenge? It is live now &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":rocket:"&gt;🚀&lt;/span&gt;... April (Citizen) Developer Challenge – SAP Build Apps: Task 0 - &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-builders-discussions/april-citizen-developer-challenge-sap-build-apps-task-0/m-p/13654312" target="_blank"&gt;https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-builders-discussions/april-citizen-developer-challenge-sap-build-apps-task-0/m-p/13654312&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Now, some cool stats on community members' participation:&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;A total of 36 SAP Community members took part in the challenge.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Unique SAP community members participation per week:&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;TABLE border="1"&gt;&lt;TBODY&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Week&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Total submissions&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;Week 1&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;31&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;Week 2&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;26&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;Week 3&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;23&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;Week 4&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;16&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;EM&gt;Total&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;EM&gt;96&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;/TBODY&gt;&lt;/TABLE&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Total submissions per week. &lt;EM&gt;Note: In week 2 a couple of participants submitted more than one solution and in weeks 3 and 4, I'm counting as valid submissions any valid message received. Many participants submitted more than one message.&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;TABLE border="1" width="100%"&gt;&lt;TBODY&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Week&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Total submissions&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;Week 1&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;31&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;Week 2&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;28&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;Week 3&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;70&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;Week 4&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD width="50%"&gt;98&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;TR&gt;&lt;TD&gt;&lt;EM&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Total&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;TD&gt;&lt;EM&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;227&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/TD&gt;&lt;/TR&gt;&lt;/TBODY&gt;&lt;/TABLE&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Last but certainly not least... a special mention to all the SAP Community members who completed the challenge every single week &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":party_popper:"&gt;🎉&lt;/span&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/45643"&gt;@Alpesa1990&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/11471"&gt;@MatLakaemper&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/789"&gt;@MioYasutake&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1395282"&gt;@Nagarajan-K&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/3763"&gt;@PriyankaChak&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/120859"&gt;@Ruthiel&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/151481"&gt;@ajos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/43545"&gt;@emiliocampo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/9180"&gt;@geek&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/874945"&gt;@pamoli_banerjee&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/38628"&gt;@r00k13d3v&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/125253"&gt;@saitgunacorel&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/162022"&gt;@spirit2681&lt;/a&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/171996"&gt;@xavisanse&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;If you are interested in the event-driven integrations/architectures topic....&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":television:"&gt;📺&lt;/span&gt; stay tuned as there is way more coming later this year in this space.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/application-development-blog-posts/march-developer-challenge-cloudevents-it-s-a-wrap/ba-p/13654243"/>
    <published>2024-04-01T06:08:23.211000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
