    <content>&lt;P&gt;My formula is similar but I convert NetAmount to a &lt;EM&gt;NUMBER&lt;/EM&gt; inside the &lt;EM&gt;MAP&lt;/EM&gt; function...&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;pre class="lia-code-sample language-javascript"&gt;&lt;code&gt;"$" + FORMAT_LOCALIZED_DECIMAL(SUM(MAP(data.A_SalesOrderItem1,NUMBER(item.NetAmount))), "en", 2)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;and for the chart I have the following:&lt;EM&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;pre class="lia-code-sample language-javascript"&gt;&lt;code&gt;MAP(SLICE(data.A_SalesOrderItem1, 0, 5), {x: item.Material, y: NUMBER(item.NetAmount)})&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-builders-discussions/april-citizen-developer-challenge-sap-build-apps-task-2-formulas/m-p/13666555#M1320"/>
    <published>2024-04-11T09:42:48.863000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
